---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Talaxy.ai" description="Privacy policy for Talaxy.ai">
  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="section-container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-cream mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-silver-400 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: February 12, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-dark space-y-8 text-silver-300 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you use our contact form, we collect the information you provide, including your name, email address, company name, and message content. We do not collect personal data through cookies or tracking scripts beyond basic analytics.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information you submit solely to respond to your inquiry, communicate about our services, and improve our offerings. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">3. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
          <p>Form submissions are processed through Web3Forms, a GDPR-compliant service that transmits data over HTTPS. We store your information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was collected.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>Our website may use the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-silver-400">
            <li>Web3Forms — for contact form processing</li>
            <li>Vercel — for website hosting and analytics</li>
            <li>Google Fonts — for typography</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@talaxy.ai" class="text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors">hello@talaxy.ai</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl text-cream mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@talaxy.ai" class="text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors">hello@talaxy.ai</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
